"an SPA leaks it, alongside the client id and secret, the attacker can\n"
"refresh and use access tokens to access the API for a long time. Therefore, "
"if you are concerned about SPA, such as a custom GPT, possibly leaking this "
"information, add `quarkus.oidc-proxy.allow-refresh-token=false` to the "
